# Sprint 9 deploy — force LF line endings on artifacts that Linux containers
# read directly. CRLF in a Caddyfile / compose file / Dockerfile / .env will
# confuse parsers in subtle ways (Caddy turns CR into part of the directive
# name; compose may misparse env values; dotenv-cli treats CR as part of the
# value). Source files (.ts/.tsx) keep the default text=auto.

* text=auto

# Deploy artifacts
Dockerfile         text eol=lf
*.Dockerfile       text eol=lf
Caddyfile          text eol=lf
docker-compose*.yml text eol=lf
.dockerignore      text eol=lf
.env*              text eol=lf
*.sh               text eol=lf
*.yml              text eol=lf
*.yaml             text eol=lf
